                        <Bold><Underline><Run Text="Danger Sense"/></Underline></Bold>
                        <LineBreak/>
                        <Run Text="At 2nd level, you gain an uncanny sense of when things nearby aren't as they should be, giving you an edge when you dodge away from danger."/>
                        <LineBreak/>
                        <Run Text="You have advantage on Dexterity saving throws against effects that you can see, such as traps and spells. To gain this benefit, you can't be blinded, deafened, or incapacitated."/>
                    </TextBlock>
                </ListViewItem>

